  "style_summary_en": "The pinnacle of Tokyo kaiseki.\nLong recognized as 'Tokyo's #1 kaiseki.'\nExtreme minimalism — no more than 3 ingredients per dish, often just 1, with very light seasoning.\n\nOne of only 4 restaurants to maintain permanent Tabelog Gold status since its inception.",
  "style_summary_jp": "東京懐石の頂点。\n長年「東京懐石1位」として認められてきた存在。\nミニマリズムの極致 — 一皿に食材3つ以下、通常1つ、非常に控えめな味付け。\n\nTabelog Gold発足以来、永久維持メンバーとして選ばれたわずか4店のうちの1つ。",
  "holistic_signature_en": "Living standard of Tokyo kaiseki.\nMinimalism + ingredient purity.",
  "holistic_signature_jp": "東京懐石の生きる基準。\nミニマル + 素材本来の正統。"
